  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_ad16eb94d5e87cc833a65630c7ad0c2e">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>Collection includes sketchbooks, examples of Boyd's graphic designs, binders documenting his best known art pieces and course material, including slides.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_c4b6c484df0fbf28a5cd2f03faa93632">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Professor emeritus in the Department of Design and Environmental Analysis in the College of Human Ecology from 1968-1995.  During this time he continued to maintain a studio in New York City and his art is included in over 400 public or private collections.  Born 1936, died in 2015.</p>  </bioghist>
  <prefercite audience="internal" id="aspace_46a6eaf7b26016be2bba69ad3931e64a">
